Package: ecositer
Type: Package
Title: ecositer: tools for the analysis, standardization, and automation of NRCS ecological data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given="Nathan", family="Roe", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "nateroe@gmail.com"))
Author: Nathan Roe [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Nathan Roe <nateroe@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of functions for Natural Resource Conservation Service (NRCS) ecologists. Many of these functions build off of the AQP (https://ncss-tech.github.io/AQP/) R packages to provide improved functionality for ecologists. 
